
Add a new menu item (on item context menu)
-------------------------------------------
 1. src/form/MainWindow.ui	Create a new xml node here!
 2. src/mainwindow.cpp		connect( ... ) function ( actionname => eventname )
 				eg: EditURLToClipboard => OnURLToClipboard
 3. src/mainwindow.cpp		EntryView->ContextMenu->addAction( ... )
 4. src/lib/EntryView.cpp	Write the function ( OnURLToClipboard )
 5. src/lib/EntryView.h		Write the functions prototype ( OnURLToClipboard)

